> >>to Top Posting, HTML composition, line wrapping pastes).
> >>
> >>It's the mindset; fixing Thunderbird is probably easy, but convincing the 
> >>Mozilla developers to include such "fixes" is probably much harder.
> >>
> >> 
> >>
